<L>__{exterior staircase night (late summer `95)}
<A>__{the lamborghini is parked at the bottom, twenty steps down. he starts to crawl down the stairs, stops. tries again. can't figure out how to do it.}
<C>__{jordan }
<D>__{fuck! the kid makes it look so easy!}
<A>__{an icy wind blows through his t shirt.}
<C>__{jordan }
<D>__{think, you motherfucker, think!}
<P>__{(a few beats; then)}
<D>__{wait, i've got it!}
<A>__{jordan slowly curls himself into a ball.}
<C>__{jordan }
<D>__{i can roll!}
<A>__{forcing himself over the edge, jordan begins to descend the steps, one at a time. thump. thump. then faster. thump thump thump. faster still. he loses control, takes all the steps at once. thump thump thump thump thump thump. he lands with a crash on the asphalt, drags himself up and into the lamborghini.}
